    "Moreover, many outliers need to be handled properly, and the dataset is not properly distributed.",
    "Outlier classification is a critical issue in machine learning because certain data samples may have considerably different features than others in the same class, and so get isolated from the rest of the data in that class.",
    "As a result, we used the Interquartile Range (IQR) technique to find outliers in this study 62.",
    "IQR can eliminate outliers by dividing a rank-ordered sample into four equal halves, known as quartiles, and evaluating dispersion.",
    "Q1 and Q3 denote the middle value in the first and second halves of the rank-ordered dataset, respectively, while Q2 is the median value for the whole set."
  ],
